title: Ultimate Xperience - The Night Creatures (Teaser)
description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

First unmastered preview from the forthcoming Ultimate Xperience double-CD album - The Realm Of A New Dawn, featuring track 'The Night Creatures' from second CD 'Ad Vitam Aaeternam'. Original track lenght is 10:24.

Written and produced by Kris Kylven
